This project provides some scripts and configuration files JUST for me

coloredlogcat.pytxt is written by Jeff Sharkey, he works for Google,
his weblog is:
http://jsharkey.org/blog/

http://jsharkey.org/blog/2009/04/22/modifying-the-android-logcat-stream-for-full-color-debugging/


$ adb logcat | ~/coloredlogcat.py
$ ~/coloredlogcat.py
